; Coverage for item.cc status/state function

2024/01/01 * Cleared
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 ! Pending
    Expenses:Food    $5.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/03 Normal
    Expenses:Food    $3.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(status) %(state) %(account)\n" Expenses
1 1 Expenses:Food
2 2 Expenses:Food
0 0 Expenses:Food
end test
